title: What type of fish are caught from the creek beside Princess Place near the cemetary?
text:
I found one reference to fishing for mullet in Burnt Mill Creek:
http://www.starnewsonline.com/article/20070514/NEWS/70514002?p=all&tc=pgall



Most references to the creek mention that it's the most degraded
creek in the Wilmington area. Usually references are to dead fish
floating on the surface.
